{"tid":2114844,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「台灣」新增一境外移入確診個案 為常居香港國人","createTime":"2020-07-19T06:22:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T06:22:22.000Z","uid":49316,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"675057208e61c202b1b94cd0544e63a983b14a95","tid":2114844,"uid":49316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T06:22:03.000Z","msg":"為港增光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎繼我國於周四、周五連續兩天新增三名境外移入病例，皆為來自菲律賓的境外移入個案後，今天再新增一名新冠肺炎境外移入病例，為40多歲男性，長期居住香港，於7月17日獨自從香港返國探親，並於今日確診。<br />\n<br />\n指揮中心發言人莊人祥表示，個案因工作長期居住香港，前次自台灣出境時間為今年4月，7月15日開始出現乾咳、喉嚨痛症狀，未就醫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/120940/4713571\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F120940%2F4713571&d=Se3jk6qONbDe%2BTgec%2FNeBx0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=1f88ef6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/120940/4713571</a>"},{"pid":"770eea6fabc0a087db5d52167ff081474cd1a87f","tid":2114844,"uid":259088,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T06:22:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}